%F A006003 Euler transform of length 3 sequence [5, 0, -1]. - _Michael Somos_, Dec 25 2016
%F A006003 a(n) = A037270(n)/n for n > 0. - _Kritsada Moomuang_, Dec 15 2018
%F A006003 a(n) = 3*A000292(n-1) + n. - _Bruce J. Nicholson_, Nov 23 2019
